1
00:00:15,583 --> 00:00:17,291
[TENCHI]
Sorry about this, Kawanagare.

2
00:00:17,375 --> 00:00:19,166
I hate to have you use
your precious break time

3
00:00:19,250 --> 00:00:20,750
showing me around the school.

4
00:00:20,833 --> 00:00:22,625
No big deal.
Don't worry about it.

5
00:00:22,708 --> 00:00:25,416
It's all in a day's work for
the Student Council President.

6
00:00:25,500 --> 00:00:27,250
I do appreciate it.

7
00:00:27,333 --> 00:00:28,708
And, uh...

8
00:00:30,291 --> 00:00:32,166
...the rest of you
are okay with this?

9
00:00:32,250 --> 00:00:33,333
Oh, absolutely!

10
00:00:33,416 --> 00:00:34,875
Supporting the President
is one of the jobs

11
00:00:34,958 --> 00:00:36,333
of the Vice-President.

12
00:00:37,708 --> 00:00:40,000
[SARYU] Unless, of course,
you and the President

13
00:00:40,083 --> 00:00:42,333
would rather have this
time all to yourselves.

14
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:45,333
That's not what I was saying!

15
00:00:45,416 --> 00:00:46,375
[FUEYAMA]
Entering data.

16
00:00:46,458 --> 00:00:47,875
Tenchi Masaki
wants solitary time

17
00:00:47,958 --> 00:00:49,208
with the Council President.

18
00:00:49,291 --> 00:00:50,833
Why are you putting
that in your records?

19
00:00:50,916 --> 00:00:52,458
Gathering data around the campus

20
00:00:52,541 --> 00:00:55,041
is one of my most important
duties as Treasurer.

21
00:00:56,083 --> 00:00:58,250
--I see, but there's been a mi--
--[HACHIKO] You pervert!

22
00:00:58,333 --> 00:01:00,916
Why are you trying to get
Mistress Momo alone?

23
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:03,416
I won't let you lay
a single finger on her!

24
00:01:03,500 --> 00:01:05,000
That's my duty as auditor!

25
00:01:05,791 --> 00:01:07,541
You're sure this is all
coming from your position

26
00:01:07,625 --> 00:01:09,041
as auditor?

27
00:01:09,125 --> 00:01:12,000
